      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and chop your<strong> red onion[s]</strong> into thin wedges</p><p>Trim your <strong>green beans</strong></p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-2-1720682714276-x200.jpg",
