      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pork has browned, add the<strong> onion wedges</strong> to the pan with the <strong>sliced pepper </strong>and<strong> trimmed beans</strong></p><p>Cook for 4-5 min, stirring occasionally to prevent burning, or until the vegetables have softened and browned</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
