    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> peanut butter </strong>with 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and mix until fully combined</p><p>Add your <strong>Thai red curry paste</strong> with your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong></p><p>Stir it all together – this is your <strong>peanut sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
