      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened and browned, add the<strong> peanut sauce </strong>to the pan and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Bring to the boil, then reduce the heat to medium and cook for a final 2-3 min or until the sauce has thickened and the beans are tender with a bite – this is your <strong>spicy Thai-style peanutty pork</strong></p>",
